translation[9]{c,v,t}:
  11,20,"Ŵanganyao nganaŵa ŵanti nikunnepelekasya (Allah kwapa ipotesi) pachilambo, soni nganakola nkwaagosa jwalijose jwangaŵaga Allah, ilagasyo ichijonjechesyedwa kukwao (ligongo lyakwasochelesya achimijao), nganaŵa nkukombola kupikana (yakuona) soni nganaŵa nkuiwona"
  11,21,"Ŵanganyao ni aŵala ŵaalijonasile achimisyene (pakulijinjisya ku Moto), soni ni ichasokonechela ayila yaŵaliji nkuisepelela (kuŵa milungu jao)"
  11,22,Pangali kaichila yanti ŵanganyao ku Akhera tachiŵa ŵakwasika nnope
  11,23,"Chisimu aŵala ŵaakulupilile ni kutendaga yambone ni kuujila mwakulinandiya kwa M’mbuje gwao, ŵanganyao niŵandu ŵa ku Mbepo, ŵanyao kwalakweko takaŵe ŵandamo"
  11,24,"Chilandanyo chamikutula jiŵiliji (makafili ni Asilamu) chili chisawu (mundu) jwangalola soni jwangapikana, ni jwakulolaga soni jwakupikanaga, ana ŵaŵiliŵa mpaka aŵe yalumo (kaŵe kao) nkwalandanyamo? Ana ngankuchetelela"
  11,25,"Soni chisimu chene twantumisye Nuhu ku ŵandu ŵakwe (nijwatite): “Chisimu une kukwenu ni nkutetela jwakuonechela.”"
  11,26,“Mwanti ngasin’galagatila (chinepe) ikaŵeje Allah. Chisimu une ngun’jogopela ilagasyo ya Lisiku Lyakupoteka nnope.”
  11,27,"Basi achinkulungwa aŵala ŵaŵakanile mwa ŵandu ŵakwe ŵatite: “Ngatukum’bonatu mmwe ikaŵeje mundu mpela uwwewe, soni ngatukum’bonatu kuti ankuyiye ikaŵeje aŵala ŵali ŵapasi petu, (soni ankuyiye) naganisyape (nkanachetelele yenumwe), soni ngatukuuona kukwenu uchimbichimbi ni umbone uliose wakutupunda uwwe, nambo tukun’ganichisya jenumanja kuti ŵaunami.”"
  11,28,"Jwalakwe jwatite: “E ŵandu ŵangu! Nkuiona uli, nimbaga une ndili pachilosyo chakuonechela chakuumila kwa Ambuje ŵangu, soni ni ambele ukoto (utume) kuumila Kukwakwe, basi ni upupuliganyisyidwe kukwenu (ukotowo), ana uwwe nimpaka tunkanganichisye walakwe (ukotowo) kutendaga jenumanja n’di nkuuchima?”"